A premier private healthcare provider in Bangalore, Jyotsna Hospital established in 2020 with the goal of providing world-class medical service to the community. The 120-bed, acute care, general medical/surgical private hospital has state-of-the-art facilities and an experienced team of healthcare professionals specialized in more than 30 medical and surgical specialties assuring comprehensive care. All physicians at jyotsna Hospital are Medical Board Certified or equivalent ensuring that patients receive international standard of care in India.
